Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.71,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Na viceprezidenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.79,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Prosím, premysli si to otče.
